" Add additional DNS Nameservers on App Server 01

" Login to App Server 01
$ ssh tony@stapp01 

" Switch to super user
$ sudo su

" Go to file path /etc/resolv.conf and add the entries
# vi /etc/resolv.conf

nameserver 8.8.8.8
nameserver 8.8.8.4

" Confirm by pinging 

$ ping google.com 

" Number of packets transmitted should be equal to the number of packets received